Package org.dapper.server.flow

A package for Dapper internal flow structures.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CountDown<T>
    Defines a count down structure.
    EmbeddingCodelet
    An extension of Codelet that surveys its input to determine embedding parameters on the client side and doubles as a FlowBuilder for embedding a subflow on the server side.
    FlowBuilder
    Defines a builder for Flows.
    FlowEdge
    An edge class representing the output-input relationship between two FlowNodes.
    Renderable
    Defines something that can render itself to a string.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractCountDown<T>
    An implementation of CountDown that leaves the CountDown.reset() method abstract.
    DummyEdge
    A edge class that represents the dummy relationship between two FlowNodes.
    Flow
    A class for storing the flow computation state.
    FlowNode
    A node class for storing Codelet computation state.
    FlowUtilities
    A static utility class for Flow bookkeeping.
    HandleEdge
    An edge class that represents the handle output-input relationship between two FlowNodes.
    LogicalEdge
    An edge class that represents the relationship between two LogicalNodes.
    LogicalNode
    A logical node class for grouping FlowNodes into functional equivalence classes.
    StreamEdge
    An edge class that represents the TCP stream relationship between two FlowNodes.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FlowEdge.FlowEdgeType
    An enumeration of FlowEdge types.
    FlowStatus
    An enumeration of Flow states.
    LogicalNodeStatus
    An enumeration of LogicalNode states.
